data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to this stunning townhome offering westerly facing intracoastal views and the added bonus of a DEEDED BOAT SLIP with a boat lift! This exquisite property boasts 3 generously sized bedrooms, each featuring its own full ensuite bathroom. A recent remodel has breathed new life into this home, with freshly painted interiors, Lifeproof vinyl flooring, upgraded baseboards, interior doors, and hardware. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring light shaker cabinetry, elegant granite countertops, a glass backsplash, top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, a range hood, and a spacious island with seating for up to six. Brand new hurricane-rated sliders open to a rear patio, creating an idyllic outdoor space for entertaining while enjoying stunning sunset views. The metal railings on the staircase have also been recently updated. A brand new roof adds peace of mind to this already exceptional property. The convenience of upper-level laundry is a welcome feature. The master bedroom is a true sanctuary with vaulted ceilings, new windows, double closets, and captivating intracoastal views. The master bath has been thoughtfully updated with double vanities, a linen tower, and a spacious walk-in shower. Boating enthusiasts will delight in the new dock with a 10k boat lift equipped with electric and water, capable of accommodating up to a 27-foot boat. Recent dredging and bank restoration ensure the slip is in top condition. Tara Cay II is a charming, small community tucked away, offering a heated pool, welcoming residents of all ages, and being pet-friendly. The low HOA fees of just $350 per month cover water, sewage, garbage, cable, internet, ground maintenance, and pool access. Current mortgage is VA assumable at 2.5%- inquire for further details. This is the ultimate opportunity to embrace the Florida lifestyle!
